m-origin: center center; text-size-adjust: 100%;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: content-box; transform-origin: center center; text-size-adjust: 100%;\"><font color=\"#000000\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: text_2; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: content-box; transform-origin: center center; text-size-adjust: 100%;\">Infrared Mode</strong>&nbsp;(Advanced IR algorithms provide clear black-and-white pictures even in darkness.)</font></span></p></li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: content-box; transform-origin: center center; text-size-adjust: 100%;\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: content-box; transform-origin: center center; text-size-adjust: 100%;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: content-box; transform-origin: center center; text-size-adjust: 100%;\"><font color=\"#000000\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: text_2; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: content-box; transform-origin: center center; text-size-adjust: 100%;\">Color Mode</strong>&nbsp;(Thanks to the two built-in spotlights, your night vision is now lit up and in full-color. Color Mode also offers outdoor lighting for your home.)</font></span></p></li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: content-box; transform-origin: center center; text-size-adjust: 100%;\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: content-box; transform-origin: center center; text-size-adjust: 100%;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: content-box; transform-origin: center center; text-size-adjust: 100%;\"><font color=\"#000000\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: text_2; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: content-box; transform-origin: center center; text-size-adjust: 100%;\">Smart Mode</strong>&nbsp;(If you switch to the Smart Mode, you can enjoy black and white night vision. The spotlights automatically turn on upon detection of suspicious motion, which shows you vivid full-color image when something happens.)</font></span></p></li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: content-box; transform-origin: center center; text-size-adjust: 100%;\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: content-box; transform-origin: center center; text-size-adjust: 100%;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: content-box; transform-origin: center center; text-size-adjust: 100%;\"><font color=\"#000000\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: text_2; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: content-box; transform-origin: center center; text-size-adjust: 100%;\">Off Mode</strong>&nbsp;(Provided that there’s no needs for outdoor lighting at night, switch to the Off Mode to avoid any light pollution.)</font></span></p></li></ul><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: text; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: content-box; transform-origin: center center; text-size-adjust: 100%;\"><font color=\"#000000\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: content-box; transform-origin: center center; text-size-adjust: 100%;\"><br><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: text_2; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: content-box; transform-origin: center center; text-size-adjust: 100%;\">Human Detection</strong><br>Powerful image processing technology quickly finds human targets in images and immediately sends a notification to your smartphone, allowing you to monitor what matters without receiving annoying false alerts.<br><br><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: text_2; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: content-box; transform-origin: center center; text-size-adjust: 100%;\">1080P Full HD Video &amp; H.265 Compression</strong><br>The 1080P sensor and advanced IR algorithms provide crystal clear video both day and night. The cutting-edge H.265 compression reduces network bandwidth and storage usage by 50% at the same video quality.<br><br><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: text_2; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: content-box; transform-origin: center center; text-size-adjust: 100%;\">Built-in Spotlights</strong><br>When the camera detects intrusion, with built-in spotlights, Bullet 2E actively keeps unwelcome visitors away from what you care before you notice them.<br><br><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: text_2; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: content-box; transfor