parent; box-sizing: content-box; transform-origin: center center; text-size-adjust: 100%;\">Note!&nbsp;</strong>IMOU IPC-A22EP-A uses soft AP to connect WiFi.<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: text_2; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: content-box; transform-origin: center center; text-size-adjust: 100%;\"><br><br>Human Detection</strong><br>Powerful image processing technology quickly finds human targets in images and immediately sends a notification to your smartphone, allowing you to monitor what matters without receiving annoying false alerts<br><br><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: text_2; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: content-box; transform-origin: center center; text-size-adjust: 100%;\">1080P Full HD Video &amp; H.265 Compression</strong><br>The 1080P sensor and advanced IR algorithms provide crystal clear video both day and night.The cutting-edge H.265 compression reduces network bandwidth and storage usage by 50% at the same video quality.<br><br><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: text_2; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: content-box; transform-origin: center center; text-size-adjust: 100%;\">0 to 355° Pan &amp; -5° to 80° Tilt</strong><br>Rotate the camera to view every corner of your home. Full range ensures no blind spots.<br><br><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: text_2; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: content-box; transform-origin: center center; text-size-adjust: 100%;\">Smart Tracking</strong><br>The camera automatically tracks and records activity when triggered by motion<br><br><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: text_2; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: content-box; transform-origin: center center; text-size-adjust: 100%;\">Privacy Mode</strong><br>Only one click on the mobile app to cover the camera lens, protecting your personal privacy when you are home.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: text; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: content-box; transform-origin: center center; text-size-adjust: 100%; color: rgb(31, 43, 53);\"><br><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: text_2; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: content-box; transform-origin: center center; text-size-adjust: 100%;\">Built-in Siren</strong><br>With the built-in siren, scare unwelcome strangers away.<br><br><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: text_2; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: content-box; transform-origin: center center; text-size-adjust: 100%;\">Abnormal Sound Alarm</strong><br>Sends instant alerts to your smartphone whenever it detects a baby crying or other abnormal sounds, keeping you aware of what\'s going on at home from anywhere.<br><br><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-styl