(426, 'Bitfenix NOVA MESH TG White Gaming Case', 'bitfenix-nova-mesh-tg-white-gaming-case', '#477845611425', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'fast_deals', 'Fast Deals', 1, 17, 0, 1, 94, 'Bitfenix-NOVA-MESH-TG-White-Gaming-Case83.jpg', 3, '<p><strong>KEY FEATURES:</strong></p><p>Support: Mini-ITX, MicroATX, ATX, E-ATX<br>Sleek Design With Mesh Front Panel<br>Material Steel, Mesh, Plastic<br>4mm Tempered Glass Side Panel</p>', '<h3 style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">Bitfenix NOVA MESH TG White Gaming Case</h3><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Bitfenix NOVA MESH TG White Gaming Case offer the best balance of performance, looks and ease of use. It represents not only BitFenix’s long standing theme of simple elegance, but also the dedication towards offering a well rounded PC chassis. It provides you well balanced between a perfectly organized interior structure and the sleek exterior design complemented with smoked tempered glass side panel. This stylish casing is built with Steel, Mesh, Plastic material. The Bitfenix NOVA MESH TG supports Mini-ITX, MicroATX, ATX, E-ATX up to 272mm(10.7 inch) motherboard. This casing comes with a high-quality tempered glass side panel with a strength of 4mm and see-through-tinted, exhibiting the often RGB illuminated core components. This casing is an all-rounder offering great airflow coupled with modern elegant design which makes it an ideal choice for most user scenarios. The NOVA MESH offers a great balance in performance and looks in it’s class with clean interior, optimized airflow and extensive compatibility. It is specifically design with ease of use in mind with easy installation and maintenance features and Its design boasts of multiple features that enhance the ease of installation and use such as the, user friendly installation, noise dampening material, removable high density mesh dust filter and dual chamber 