if; font-size: 14px;\"><br></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Construction</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">The VSK3000 Elite is constructed to be a versatile case that is easy to work with. The VSK3000 Elite supports up to micro-ATX motherboards and has four expansion slots and ample room for hard drives, all while having space to accommodate VGA cards up to 13 inches (335 mm). If you’re looking for a simple, reliable case that won’t break the bank, the VSK3000 Elite fits the bill</div>', 0, 1, '2550', '2300', NULL, 0, '2021-08-24 23:55:16', '2021-09-07 07:17:23'),
