(434, 'Antec P110 Luce Mid-Tower With Tempered Glass RGB Gaming Casing', 'antec-p110-luce-mid-tower-with-glass-rgb-gaming-casing', '#218252273433', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'fast_deals', 'Fast Deals', 1, 17, 0, 1, 95, 'Antec-P110-Luce-Mid-Tower-With-Tempered-Glass-RGB-Gaming-Casing96.jpg', 7, '<p><strong>Key features:</strong></p><p>Type: Steel ATX Mid Tower<br>Support: Micro ATX / ATX<br>DIM: 20.39\" x 9.06\" x 19.25\"<br>Weight : 25.80 lbs.</p>', '<h3 style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">Antec P110 Luce Mid-Tower With Tempered Glass RGB Gaming Casing</h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">The P110 Luce combines versatility and performance with refined craftsmanship for a sleek, VR-ready mid tower that features an adjustable VGA holder, cable management bar, and removable drive bays, for outstanding flexibility and customization. The innovative radiator mounting position lets you take advantage of every bit of space available in the interior, making the P110 Luce an easy choice for your custom watercooled rig. The tempered glass side panels highlight the components within, and the built-in RGB controller changes lighting modes and colors with ease.<br></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">CUSTOMIZE YOUR LIGHTING EFFECTS</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">The unparalleled styling of the P110 Luce is finished with a tempered glass side panel, and the built-in RGB controller lets you plug LED light strips to customize your look. Let you rig shine bright with various lighting effects and cycle through seven colors with the RGB controller 