(465, 'Lian Li LANCOOL II RGB ATX Mid Tower Gaming Case (White)', 'lian-li-lancool-ii-rgb-atx-mid-tower-gaming-case-white', '#67743375464', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'fast_deals', 'Fast Deals', 1, 17, 0, 1, 98, 'Lian-Li-LANCOOL26.jpg', 4, '<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p><p>Model: LANCOOL II<br>Removable Two-way Cable Management Bar<br>Exquisite Steel Craftsmanship<br>Cable management at ease<br>Flip panels &amp; shrouds all around</p>', '<h3 style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">Lian Li LANCOOL II RGB ATX Mid Tower Gaming Case (White)</h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify;\">The Lian Li LANCOOL II RGB case is born to perform with powerful multifunctional well-crafted. This one of the ultimate x. This case is comes with Exquisite Steel Craftsmanship with 35mm wide front mesh for optimized airflow. Flip Panels and All Around. The Flip panels &amp; shrouds all around: equipped with hinged tempered glass panels as well as two metallic shroud panels, eliminating the need for unnecessary screws. Here the tempered glass side panels offer an unobstructed view to the internal components and also at the bottom shround panel provide a quick and easy access to hard drive installation, the flip power supply shrouds at both sides offer a quick and easy access to storage drive installation. Cable management at ease also added in this case. Reversable two-way cable management bar also include here, It not only serves as cable management bar but also allows users to fit an ATX/E-ATX motherboard. In this gaminge case, it also designed with Two cover plates behind the motherboard tray to conceal nearly all cables. This latest gaming case designed with 0.8mm SGCC (Exterior, MB tray, and most of the interior), 4.0mm tempered glass (both sides), Front (multi-way fan/radiator bracket): 3 X 120mm or 2 X 140mm, Above PSU Chamber: 2 X 120mm, Top: 2 X 120/140mm, Rear: 1 X 120mm, Front (multi-way fan/radiator bracket): 1 X 360/280/240mm, Top: 1 X 240mm (aligned to the left) Radiator, 384mm VGA Length, 176mm CPU Clearance, Behind MB Tray: 2 X 2.5″ SSD, Hard Drive Cage: 3 X 3.5″ HDD/2.5″ SSD, Behind the Right-side Shroud Panel: 2 X 2.5″ SSD; 1 x Top (magnetic), 1 x Front Panel (magnetic), 1 x Bottom (tray) Dust Filters and include 3 X 120mm (Front, Top, Rear) Fan. The Fan &amp; cooling optimization: capable to support overall 8 x 120mm fans, a 360mm radiator at the front and a 240mm radiator at the top, Tool-less RGB front panel and Easy access to RGB light control through the C and M buttons on the top panel.</p>', 0, 1, '9000', '8800', NULL, 0, '2021-08-29 00:02:59', '2021-09-07 02:54:11'),
(466, 'Lian Li LANCOOL II RGB ATX Mid Tower Gaming Case (Black)', 'lian-li-lancool-ii-rgb-atx-mid-tower-gaming-case-black', '#268729697465', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'fast_deals', 'Fast Deals', 1, 17, 0, 1, 98, 'xyz12.jpg', 4, '<p><strong>KEY FEATURES:</strong></p><p>Model: LANCOOL II Mesh RGB<br>Motherboard Type: E-ATX/ ATX/M-ATX/ITX<br>4.0mm tempered glass (both sides)<br>Slot: 7, PSU: 210mm<br>Honeycomb vent design &amp; RGB fans</p>', '<h3 itemprop=\"name\" class=\"product-name\" style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">Lian Li LANCOOL II Mesh RGB Gaming Case (White)</h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify;\">The Lian Li LANCOOL II Mesh RGB Case features with a mesh front panel and mesh bottom left shroud panel, honeycomb vent design and built-in RGB fans. It is also ensuring bountiful airflow delivered to your high-performance components while adorning the system with an RGB touch. This new Lian Li LANCOOL II Mesh casing designed with Premium look, Unprecedented modularity, Hinged flip panels all around, Optimized cooling support, Cable management with ease and Optimized storage configuration. In this case, the optimized airflow is a result of the collaboration between the brand-new mesh design, additional exhaust vent holes, and also three high-performance ARGB cooling fans. It is also comes with 3 x 120mm ARGB intake fans pre-installed at the front produce ample airflow while still offering bountiful RGB to liven up your PC build and also give u ultimate coolinf support. In this casing, the Lighting effects of the 3 included ARGB fans can be fully controlled through the C button and M button located on the top front. Switching between 8 lighting modes has never been this easy. The space between the top and bottom chamber now features two removable PSU shroud covers for either 2 x 2.5” SSDs or can be removed to fit 2 x 120mm fans. Here, the multi-way bracket revolutionizes your notion of fan/radiator installation by offering 4 installation options to best fit your needs. In this case, The multi-way bracket revolutionizes your notion of fan/radiator installation by offering 4 installation options to best fit your need. It is also comes with the modular drive cage, side-mounted SSD bays, and additional SSD space on the modular PSU shroud cover, the LANCOOL II MESH is capable of holding up to 9 drives. In this exclusive casing, the tempered glass side panels offer an unobstructed view to the interior configuration while the bottom shroud panels provide quick access to PSU/drive installation and also the cover plates save users’ neck and fingers by concealing nearly all the wayward cables.</p>', 0, 1, '9000', '8600', NULL, 0, '2021-08-29 00:38:58', '2021-09-07 06:48:20'),
(467, 'ASUS TUF Gaming VG279Q1A 27\" FHD Gaming Monitor', 'asus-tuf-gaming-vg279q1a-27-fhd-gaming-monitor', '#92812928466', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'fast_deals', 'Fast Deals', 1, 17, 0, 1, 12, 'ASUS-TUF-Gaming-VG279Q1A-27-FHD-Gaming-Monitor99.jpg', 7, '<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p><p>Model: TUF Gaming VG279Q1A<br>FHD (1920 x 1080) IPS Panel with ultrafast 165Hz refresh rate<br>ASUS Extreme Low Motion Blur (ELMB ) technology<br>1ms response time (MPRT)<br>Adaptive-sync &amp; FreeSync</p>', '<h3 style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">ASUS TUF Gaming VG279Q1A 27\" FHD Gaming Monitor</h3><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">The ASUS TUF Gaming VG279Q1A 27\" FHD Gaming Monitor is a 27-inch Full HD (1920 x 1080) IPS display that comes with an ultrafast 165Hz refresh rate. Designed for gamers and others seeking immersive gameplay. Its exclusive ELMB function features a 1ms MPRT response time and Adaptive-Sync (FreeSync Premium) technology, for extremely fluid gameplay without tearing and stuttering. It delivers stunning visuals from all angles with wide 178-degree viewing angles that ensure minimal distortion and color shift even when you\'re viewing from extreme positions. This monitor Features the latest ASUS-exclusive Extreme Low Motion Blur technology, which achieves 1ms MPRT to eliminate smearing and motion blur, and makes objects in motion look sharper, so gameplay is more fluid and responsive. The TUF Gaming VG279Q1A has a stealth fighter-inspired design that gives it a dynamic, futuristic look. The rear panel features wing-like elements, giving it a sensation of speed. A svelte, minimalist stand ensures stability and a touch of elegance. Extensive connectivity options, including Displa