(483, 'Edifier M1390BT Speaker', 'edifier-m1390bt-speaker', '#503070348482', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'fast_deals', 'Fast Deals', 1, 136, 0, 1, 100, 'Edifier-M1390BT-Speaker88.jpg', 4, '<p><strong>KEY FEATURES:</strong></p><p>Switch between Bluetooth or auxiliary control at your convenience<br>Front-facing reflex bass port for detailed audio output<br>2.75 inch (70mm) full range satellite speakers<br>5 inch (131mm) subwoofer with adjustable bass</p>', '<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.41575em; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;IBM Plex Sans&quot;; font-size: 17px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 600; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Attractive design and sound</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.41575em; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;IBM Plex Sans&quot;; font-size: 17px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">The housing of the satellites has a luxurious look. The molded plastic housing has a thickened shell which is very stable and reduces the resonance, for better sound quality.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.41575em; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;IBM Plex Sans&quot;; font-size: 17px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 600; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Powerful design</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.41575em; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;IBM Plex Sans&quot;; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Low-frequency sound is well represented by the subwoofer with a 5-inch speaker driver. This is magnetic proof. The MDF wooden subwoofer is stable and of good thickness, which effectively reduces resonance.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.41575em; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;IBM Plex Sans&quot;; font-size: 17px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 600; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Full range satellite driver</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.41575em; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;IBM Plex Sans&quot;; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">The satellites are equipped with 2.75 inch (70mm) full range drivers. The cone is made of a special composite material that optimally reproduces both the middle and the high frequencies.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.41575em; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;IBM Plex Sans&quot;; font-size: 17px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 600; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Easy to operate</span><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">With the multi-function button , you can control the volume and put the speakers in standby mode, and switch between the Aux and Bluetooth.</p>', 0, 1, '7300', '6999', NULL, 0, '2021-08-30 23:56:14', '2021-09-08 22:53:17'),
(484, 'Edifier X230BT Speaker', 'edifier-x230bt-speaker', '#216864479483', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'fast_deals', 'Fast Deals', 1, 136, 0, 1, 100, 'Edifier-X230BT-Speaker44.jpg', 7, '<p><strong>KEY FEATURES:</strong><br>High quality wooden sub woofer delivers deep bass<br>28 watts(RMS) of powerful, crystal-clear sound<br>LED lighting effects enhance your gaming experience<br>Inputs: Bluetooth 4.2, Line in and AUX audio input<br>Convenient control panel for easy volume and light control</p>', '<h2 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.6em; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); line-height: 1.4; font-size: 1.45em; font-family: &quot;IBM Plex Sans&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Edifier X230BT Speaker</h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.41575em; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;IBM Plex Sans&quot;; font-size: 17px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/multimediakingdom\" style=\"color: rgb(30, 115, 190); transition: color 0.2s ease 0s; touch-action: manipulation; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Edifier</a>&nbsp;X230BT&nbsp;<a href=\"https://multimediakingdom.com.bd/product-category/music-sound-accessories/speaker/computer-speakers/\" style=\"color: rgb(30, 115, 190); transition: color 0.2s ease 0s; touch-action: manipulation; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Speaker</a>&nbsp;available in Bangladesh.</p><ul style=\"padding: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.41575em; margin-left: 20px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;IBM Plex Sans&quot;; font-size: 17px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><li style=\"margin-bottom: 3px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Edifier Bluetooth 2.1 Gaming Multimedia Speaker System | AUX | RGB Lighting, Bluetooth – Black</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 3px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">2.1 gaming multimedia speaker</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 3px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">High quality wooden sub woofer delivers deep bass</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 3px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">28 watts(RMS) of powerful, crystal-clear sound</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 3px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">LED lighting effects enhance your gaming experience</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 3px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Inputs: Bluetooth 4.2, Line in and AUX audio input</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 3px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Convenient control panel for easy volume and light control</li></ul>', 0, 1, '5500', '4999', NULL, 0, '2021-08-31 15:34:37', '2021-09-19 07:45:42'),
(485, 'Edifier C2XD Speaker', 'edifier-c2xd-speaker', '#510427986484', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'fast_deals', 'Fast Deals', 1, 136, 0, 1, 100, 'Edifier-C2XD-Speaker-(1)84.jpg', 5, '<p><strong>KEY FEATURES:</strong></p><p><br>Brand:Edifier<br>Model:C2XD<br>Power output R/L: RMS 9W x 2SW: RMS 35W<br>THD + N:10%<br>Signal to noise rate:≥ 85dBA<br>Frequency response:55Hz-18kHz (±6dB)</p>', '<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.41575em; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;IBM Plex Sans&quot;; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Beautifully crafted in a modern and robust design, C2XD is an ideal audio solution for music enthusiasts and dedicated gamers alike. Armed with Edifier Electronic Intelligent Distortion Control (EIDC) technology, it dynamically manages output and avoids audio distortion when you crank up the volume. With a generous subwoofer and a stand-alone amplifier, this 2.1 speaker is engineered for rich, exhilarating sound.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.41575em; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;IBM Plex Sans&quot;; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 600; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Independent amplifier</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.41575em; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;IBM Plex Sans&quot;; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">C2XD’s amplifier is a stand-alone unit, so that the speakers can be placed optimally. Other useful features include an LCD display, and a headphone jack conveniently located on the side of the amplifier.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.41575em; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;IBM Plex Sans&quot;; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 600; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Subwoofer</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.41575em; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;IBM Plex Sans&quot;; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">The generous 6½” subwoofer produces an incredible 35 watts RMS, while the satellites produce 18 watts RMS.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.41575em; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;IBM Plex Sans&quot;; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 600; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Precise control</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.41575em; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;IBM Plex Sans&quot;; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">The wireless, multifunctional remote gives you precise control over volume, bass and treble adjustments, input selection, mute and standby. Whatever your music taste is, you are in full control.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.41575em; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;IBM Plex Sans&quot;; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 600; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Multiple input options</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.41575em; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;IBM Plex Sans&quot;; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">C2XD is equipped with optical, RCA and auxiliary input options. MP3 players, game consoles, PC and laptop, you name it. It can take whatever gadget you throw at it.</p>', 0, 1, '10000', '9600', NULL, 0, '2021-08-31 19:29:59', '2021-09-19 01:17:08'),
