=\"margin-bottom: 3px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">AUX audio input for various connection</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 3px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Edifier Electronic Intelligent Distortion Control (EIDC)</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 3px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">IR remote control for easy adjustment</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 3px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><span class=\"specs-title\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Total power output:</span>&nbsp;R/L: RMS 9W x 2SW: RMS 35W</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 3px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><span class=\"specs-title\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">THD + N:</span>&nbsp;10%</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 3px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><span class=\"specs-title\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">SNR:</span>&nbsp;≥85dBA</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 3px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><span class=\"specs-title\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Frequency Range:</span>&nbsp;55Hz-18kHz (±6dB)</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 3px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><span class=\"specs-title\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Input sensitivity:</span>&nbsp;R/L: 450mV ± 50mVSW: 150mV ± 50mV</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 3px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><span class=\"specs-title\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Dimension:</span>&nbsp;Amplifier: 250mm x 78mm x 255mm (W x H x D)</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 3px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Satellite: 130mm x 90mm x 180mm (W x H x D)</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 3px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Subwoofer: 288mm x 232mm x 242mm (W x H x D)</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 3px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><span class=\"specs-title\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Weight:</span>&nbsp;7.8Kg (net) | 8.9Kg (gross)</li></ul><div class=\"vg768-2-1 c2\" style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;IBM Plex Sans&quot;; font-size: 17px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><div class=\"text-box\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.41575em; margin-left: 0px; text-align: justify; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Beautifully crafted in a modern and robust design, C2XB is an ideal audio solution for music enthusiasts and dedicated gamers alike. Armed with Edifier Electronic Intelligent Distortion Control (EIDC) technology, it dynamically manages output and avoids audio distortion when you crank up the volume. With a generous subwoofer and a stand-alone amplifier, this 2.1 speaker is engineered for rich, exhilarating sound.</p><div class=\"vg768-2-1 c2 vg768hide\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><div class=\"text-box\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><h3 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.840791em; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 24px; letter-spacing: -0.3px; line-height: 1.55; text-align: justify; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Independent amplifier</h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.41575em; margin-left: 0px; text-align: justify; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">C2XB’s amplifier is a stand-alone unit, so that the speakers can be placed optimally. Other useful features include an LCD display, and a headphone jack conveniently located on the side of the amplifier.</p><div class=\"vg768-2-1 c2 vg768hide\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><div class=\"text-box\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><h3 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.840791em; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 24px; letter-spacing: -0.3px; line-height: 1.55; text-align: justify; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Precise control</h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.41575em; margin-left: 0px; text-align: justify; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">The wireless, multifunctional remote gives you precise control over volume, bass and treble adjustments, input selection, mute and standby. Whatever your music taste is, you are in full control.</p><div class=\"vg768-2-1 c2\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><div class=\"text-box\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><h3 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.840791em; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 24px; letter-spacing: -0.3px; line-height: 1.55; text-align: justify; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Multiple input options</h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.41575em; margin-left: 0px; text-align: justify; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">C2XB is equipped with RCA and auxiliary input options. MP3 players, game consoles, PC and laptop, you name it. It can take whatever gadget you throw at it.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>', 0, 1, '10000', '9800', NULL, 0, '2021-08-31 19:48:15', '2021-09-21 14:11:22'),
(488, 'Edifier S760D Dolby Digital Home Theater', 'edifier-s760d-dolby-digital-home-theater', '#621248140487', NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'fast_deals', 'Fast Deals', 1, 136, 0, 1, 100, 'Edifier-S760D-Dolby-Digital-Home-Theater-(1)64.jpg', 3, '<p><strong>KEY FEATURES:</strong></p><p>5.1 home theatre system with Dolby Digital, Pro Logic II and DTS<br>3 optical, 1 coaxial, analogue 5.1 and dual stereo inputs<br>Multi-functional controller and wireless remote control<br>&nbsp;</p>', '<h3 class=\"page_title\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.840791em; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 24px; font-family: &quot;IBM Plex Sans&quot;; letter-spacing: -0.3px; line-height: 1.55; text-align: justify; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Overview</span></h3><p class=\"page_text\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.41575em; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;IBM Plex Sans&quot;; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Armed with Dolby Digital, Dolby Pro Logic II and DTS sound decoders, S760D is engineered to deliver the best-possible 5.1 listening experience. With an enormous 10″ subwoofer and ground-shaking output, S760D is perfect for your favorite TV shows, movies, games and music albums.</p><div class=\"text\" style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;IBM Plex Sans&quot;; font-size: 17px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><h3 class=\"page_title\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.840791em; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 24px; letter-spacing: -0.3px; line-height: 1.55; text-align: justify; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Enormous Sub woofer</span></h3><p class=\"page_text\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.41575em; margin-left: 0px; text-align: justify; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Boasting 540 watts RMS, S760D demands its share of attention. A massive 10″ subwoofer driver and twin bass radiators deliver superb bass performance. Complemented by two-way satellite speakers with 3½” midrange drivers and 1” solk-domed tweeters.</p><p class=\"page_text\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.41575em; margin-left: 0px; text-align: justify; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">But S760’s superior sound doesn’t stop there. With the power booster function to enhance system volume, S760D is designed to instantly fill a large room with exhilarating sound. The two-way satellite speakers, with professionally calibrated crossovers, is equipped with 3.5-inch mid-range drivers and 1-inch silk dome tweeters.</p><div class=\"text\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><h3 class=\"page_title\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.840791em; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 24px; letter-spacing: -0.3px; line-height: 1.55; text-align: justify; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Wired and wireless remote controls</span></h3><p class=\"page_text\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.41575em; margin-left: 0px; text-align: justify; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">No matter where you are in the room, S760D lets you stay in full control of your sound. It features a wired remote control with LCD display and a wireless control, providing easy trimming, tuning, volume and input adjustments.</p><h3 class=\"text-title input\" style=\"margin-top: 1.29068em; margin-bottom: 0.840791em; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 24px; letter-spacing: -0.3px; line-height: 1.55; text-align: justify; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Multiple input options</span></h3><p class=\"text-tagline-med\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.41575em; margin-left: 0px; text-align: justify; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Featuring 3 optical inputs, 1 coaxial input, analog 5.1 and dual stereo inputs, S760D is a versatile speaker system for home entertainment, gaming and music, you name it.</p></div></div>', 0, 1, '64000', '61999', NULL, 0, '2021-08-31 19:50:18', '2021-09-21 15:35:45'),
(489, 'Edifier P3080M Multimedia Karaoke Speaker', 'edifier-p3080m-multimedia-karaoke-speaker', '#177429280488', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'fast_deals', 'Fast Deals', 1, 136, 0, 1, 100, 'Edifier-P3080M-Multimedia-Karaoke-Speaker-(1)25.jpg', 4, '<p><strong>KEY FEATURES:</strong></p><p>Total power output:RMS 10W x 2 + 16W x 1<br>THD + N:10%<br>SNR:≥85dBA<br>Distortion:≤0.5%</p>', '<h3 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.840791em; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 24px; font-family: &quot;IBM Plex Sans&quot;; letter-spacing: -0.3px; line-height: 1.55; text-align: justify; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Overview</span></h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.41575em; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;IBM Plex Sans&quot;; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Equipped with a microphone input and multiple connection ports, P3080M is a 2.1 multimedia speaker system designed for karaoke and so much more. The 6½” bass driver guarantees powerful bass performance, accompanied by both mid- and high-range tweeters that pack a punch.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.41575em; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;IBM Plex Sans&quot;; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">To give you the most authentic 2.1 listening experience, sound resonance in the subwoofer and satellites is minimized by wooden enclosures. So you can hear your music exactly the way it’s meant to be heard.</p><div class=\"vg768-2-1 c2 vg768hide\" style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;IBM Plex Sans&quot;; font-size: 17px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><div class=\"text-box\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><h3 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.840791em; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 24px; letter-spacing: -0.3px; line-height: 1.55; text-align: justify; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Perfect for karaoke</span></h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.41575em; margin-left: 0px; text-align: justify; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Uniquely equipped with microphone input port. P3080 is perfect for karaoke.What’s more, this beast of a system can be tuned to be exactly the way you like it, thanks to EQ controls, as well as individual microphone and master volume controls on the subwoofer.</p><div class=\"vg768-2-1 c2\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><div class=\"text-box\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><h3 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.840791em; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 24px; letter-spacing: -0.3px; line-height: 1.55; text-align: justify; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">USB input</span></h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.41575em; margin-left: 0px; text-align: justify; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Subtle in design, yet versatile in function. P3080M 2.1 speaker system can be connected to your favorite audio hosts using the 3.5mm stereo jack and the USB input port.Control keys are conveniently located on the side of the subwoofer for precise adjustments.</p></div></div></div></div>', 0, 1, '4800', '4500', NULL, 0, '2021-08-31 20:09:16', '2021-09-08 22:53:04'),
(490, 'Edifier S530D Multimedia Speaker System', 'edifier-s530d-multimedia-speaker-system', '#178245418489', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'fast_deals', 'Fast Deals', 1, 136, 0, 1, 100, 'Edifier-S530D-Multimedia-Speaker-System-(1)70.jpg', 3, '<p><strong>KEY FEATURES:</strong></p><p><br>Powerful 2.1 multimedia speaker system, with 8 inch subwoofer<br>Stereo RCA connection, Optical and Coaxil Inputs<br>Multifunctional wired controller with 2½ inch LCD display with dimmer option</p>', '<h2 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.6em; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); line-height: 1.4; font-size: 1.45em; font-family: &quot;IBM Plex Sans&quot;; text-align: justify; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Edifier S530D Multimedia Speaker System</h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.41575em; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;IBM Plex Sans&quot;; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/edifierbangladeshOfficial\" style=\"color: rgb(30, 115, 190); transition: color 0.2s ease 0s; touch-action: manipulation; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Edifier</a>&nbsp;S530D&nbsp;<a href=\"https://multimediakingdom.com.bd/product-category/music-sound-accessories/speaker/computer-speakers/\" style=\"color: rgb(30, 115, 190); transition: color 0.2s ease 0s; touch-action: manipulation; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Multimedia Speaker</a>&nbsp;System With 145 watts of awesome power, stunning sound is yours for the taking.</p><ul style=\"padding: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.41575em; margin-left: 20px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;IBM Plex Sans&quot;; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><li style=\"margin-bottom: 3px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Powerful 2.1 multimedia speaker system, with 8 inch subwoofer</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 3px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Stereo RCA connection, Optical and Coaxil Inputs</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 3px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Multifunctional wired controller with 2½ inch LCD display with dimmer option</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 3px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><span class=\"specs-title\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Total power output:</span>&nbsp;RMS 35W x 2 + 75W x 1</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 3px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><span class=\"specs-title\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">THD + N:</span>&nbsp;10%</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 3px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><span class=\"specs-title\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">SNR:</span>&nbsp;≥85dBA</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 3px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><span class=\"specs-title\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Frequency response:</span>&nbsp;Satellites: 150Hz – 20kHz</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 3px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Subwoofer: 20Hz – 120Hz</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 3px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><span class=\"specs-title\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Distortion:</span>&nbsp;≤0.5%</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 3px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><span class=\"specs-title\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Input sensitivity:</span>&nbsp;Satellites: 600mV ± 50mV (Line in)</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 3px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Subwoofer: 300mV ± 50mV (Line in)</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 3px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><span class=\"specs-title\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Input impedance:</span>&nbsp;10KΩ</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 3px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><span class=\"specs-title\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Subwoofer / bass unit:</span>&nbsp;8 inch, magnetically shielded, 4Ω</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 3px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><span class=\"specs-title\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Midrange / high unit:</span>&nbsp;3½ inch, magnetically shielded, 8Ω</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 3px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><span class=\"specs-title\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Tweeter unit:</span>&nbsp;Φ25mm silk dome, magnetically shielded, 6Ω</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 3px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><span class=\"specs-title\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Dimensions:</span>&nbsp;Subwoofer: 274mm x 309mm x 468mm</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 3px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Satellites: 116mm x 203mm x 160mm (WxHxD)</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 3px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><span class=\"specs-title\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Weight:</span>&nbsp;≈19.00Kg (net) / ≈20.70Kg (gross)</li></ul><div class=\"text-box\" style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;IBM Plex Sans&quot;; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><h3 class=\"text-title\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.840791em; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 24px; letter-spacing: -0.3px; line-height: 1.55; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Overview</h3><p class=\"text-tagline-med\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.41575em; margin-left: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Powerful and distinctive, S530D 2.1 speaker system lets you rediscover your music like you’ve never heard before. Featuring a massive subwoofer, wired and wireless remote control, and flexible connectivity, S530D packs everything you need in a functional and elegant system.</p><div class=\"text-box\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><h3 class=\"text-title\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.840791em; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 24px; letter-spacing: -0.3px; line-height: 1.55; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">145 watts of awesome power</span></h3><p class=\"text-tagline-med\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.41575em; margin-left: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">S530D features a massive 8-inch sub woofer that pumps out deep, rich bass. The satellites are equipped with 3.5-inch mid range drivers and 25mm silk-domed tweeters. Together, S530D packs 145 watts of awesome power within the 2.1 speaker system. Whether you use this 2.1 speaker system for music, PC/laptop, home theater and gaming, S530D will not disappoint.</p><div class=\"text-box white-on-white\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><h3 class=\"text-title\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.840791em; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 24px; letter-spacing: -0.3px; line-height: 1.55; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Wired, wireless control</span></h3><p class=\"text-tagline-med\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.41575em; margin-left: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">With both wired and wireless remote controls, S530D lets you adjust your sound exactly the way you like it, from any corner of the room. The wired remote features a generous 2-inch LCD display with a built-in dimmer. You will also find a headphone port on the wired remote for a more private listening experience. The multi functional wireless remote provides a full range of adjustments.</p><p class=\"text-tagline-med\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.41575em; margin-left: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">What’s more, S530D is equipped with stereo RCA connection, optical and coaxial inputs and 3.5mm line-in. So it’s ready to handle whatever device you throw at it.</p></div></div></div><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.41575em; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;IBM Plex Sans&quot;; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Edifier S530 packs 145watt of power within this 2:1 speaker system. Featuring a 2″ LCD display, multi functional wired controller for ease of volume control and a wireless remote for audio playback or jumping to the next track, the S530 can be controlled with ease. Suitable for home theater use, computer PC connectivity as well as perfect for gaming, the S530 will not disappoint.</p>', 0, 1, '42500', '40000', NULL, 0, '2021-08-31 20:16:53', '2021-09-08 22:56:09'),
(491, 'Edifier e235 Bluetooth Multimedia Speaker', 'edifier-e235-bluetooth-multimedia-speaker', '#625733680490', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'fast_deals', 'Fast Deals', 1, 136, 0, 1, 100, 'Edifier-e235-Bluetooth-Multimedia-Speaker-(1)74.jpg', 5, '<p><strong>KEY FEATURES:</strong></p><p>Award-winning 2.1 sound system<br>5.8G Wireless Subwoofer<br>Bluetooth 4.0 pairing<br>Bluetooth 4.0, Optical and Aux&nbsp;<br>Wireless Subwoofer – Massive 8&nbsp;<br>THX Certified &nbsp;<br>Remote Control&nbsp;<br>1 year warranty &nbsp;</p>', '<h3 class=\"text-title\" style=\"margin-top: 1.29068em; margin-bottom: 0.840791em; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 24px; font-family: &quot;IBM Plex Sans&quot;; letter-spacing: -0.3px; line-height: 1.55; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">AWARD-WINNING SOUND SYSTEM</h3><p class=\"text-description bounceInRight\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.41575em; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;IBM Plex Sans&quot;; font-size: 17px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Independent industrial designers, engineers and members of the trade media have given the e235 Luna E 2.1 Edifier speaker system the 2015 CES Innovation Awards Honouree. Its outstanding design and engineering have set it apart from competitors.</p><h3 class=\"text-title\" style=\"margin-top: 1.29068em; margin-bottom: 0.840791em; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 24px; font-family: &quot;IBM Plex Sans&quot;; letter-spacing: -0.3px; line-height: 1.55; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">THE POWER OF BLUETOOTH 4.0</h3><p class=\"text-description bounceInRight\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.41575em; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;IBM Plex Sans&quot;; font-size: 17px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">With a signal reception range of up to 300 feet and the use of Bluetooth 4.0 aptX this audio system achieves high-quality sound no matter where you place it. Best of all, it can be controlled from virtually anywhere in your house through your paired device.</p><p class=\"text-description bounceInRight\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.41575em; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;IBM Plex Sans&quot;; font-size: 17px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">This powerful 2.1 speaker system is THX certified with built-in Digital Signal Processing, Dynamic Range Control and 3D Sound Processing. This model also features connectivity via optical or auxiliary input port. Ideal for your Nintendo, Playstation, or Xbox console.</p><div class=\"text-box\" style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;IBM Plex Sans&quot;; font-size: 17px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><h3 class=\"text-title\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.840791em; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 24px; letter-spacing: -0.3px; line-height: 1.55; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">WIRELESS SUBWOOFER</h3><p class=\"text-description bounceInRight\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.41575em; margin-left: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">The subwoofer is wirelessly connected at a 5.8GHz radio frequency to its satellite companions. Built with two 8-inch drivers to provide clear, crisp sound. With its 100-watt built-in amplifier, the subwoofer takes your music to the next level, leaving the wires behind.</p><p class=\"text-description bounceInRight\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.41575em; margin-left: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">It’s a match made in heaven when combining the subwoofer and the 2-way satellite speakers. Designed with dual layer housing to provide outstanding sound dampening, this team provides professional sound tuning. Both satellites are equipped with a ¾” tweeter and a 3-inch driver producing 38w.</p><h3 class=\"text-title\" style=\"margin-top: 1.29068em; margin-bottom: 0.840791em; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 24px; letter-spacing: -0.3px; line-height: 1.55; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">SLEEK REMOTE AND SIMPLE TOUCH CONTROLS</h3><p class=\"text-description bounceInRight\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.41575em; margin-left: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Edifier’s e235 2.1 speaker system is controlled easily with the slick remote that accompanies the system. The small and thin remote fits right in your pocket for simple volume control.</p><p class=\"text-description bounceInRight\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.41575em; margin-left: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Closer to the speaker than the remote? Thanks to the touch sensitive controls on the e235 Edifier system, the remote is not always necessary. The touch sensitive controls on the speaker allow you to turn the system on and off, and adjust the volume without using the remote.</p><div class=\"text-box\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><h3 class=\"text-title\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.840791em; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 24px; letter-spacing: -0.3px; line-height: 1.55; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">COLOUR</h3><p class=\"text-description bounceInRight\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.41575em; margin-left: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">If red is too flashy, the award-winning sound system also comes in black, white, blue and orange to better match your home’s interior design.</p><p class=\"text-description bounceInRight\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.41575em; margin-left: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">*Colours may vary by region.</p></div></div>', 0, 1, '42500', '40000', NULL, 0, '2021-08-31 20:20:18', '2021-09-08 21:38:57'),
