t;; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">E228BU&nbsp;2:1 multimedia bluetooth speaker has excellent sound,Output Power 30w+ 10x2W(RMS), W175*H314*D387MM speaker bass driver, 3″ full range satellite driver, bluetooth 4.0 function support, plug and play USB/ SD card reader and full function remote control.This 2.1 speakers has powerful 50watt (RMS) sound that provide good bass, highs and mids.E228BU has convenient RCA and 3.5 mm inputs for music, movie and gaming devices. super big wooden cabinet subwoofer and satellites delivers heart-thumping bass, high efficient energy saving design, Also this multimedia Bluetooth Speaker comes with 1 year warranty.</p>', 0, 1, '4500', '4200', NULL, 0, '2021-08-31 20:23:59', '2021-09-08 22:53:22'),
(493, 'Creative Sound BlasterX Kratos S3 Gaming Speaker', 'creative-sound-blasterx-kratos-s3-gaming-speaker', '#300034694492', NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'fast_deals', 'Fast Deals', 1, 136, 0, 1, 102, 'Creative-Sound-BlasterX-Kratos-S3-Gaming-Speaker-(1)51.jpg', 5, '<p><strong>KEY FEATURES:</strong></p><p>92W Peak Power Audio<br>BEST-IN-CLASS 2.1 GAMING SPEAKER SYSTEM &nbsp;<br>NATURAL SOUNDING WOODEN ENCLOSURES&nbsp;<br>AUDIO CONTROLS&nbsp;<br>BLASTERX ACOUSTIC ENGINE &nbsp;</p>', '<h2 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.6em; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); line-height: 1.4; font-size: 1.45em; font-family: &quot;IBM Plex Sans&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Creative Sound BlasterX Kratos S3 Gaming Speaker</h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.41575em; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;IBM Plex Sans&quot;; font-size: 17px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Creative Sound BlasterX Kratos S3 Gaming Speaker</p><ul class=\"a-unordered-list a-vertical a-spacing-none\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.41575em; margin-left: 20px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;IBM Plex Sans&quot;; font-size: 17px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><li style=\"margin-bottom: 3px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">92W Peak Power Audio</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 3px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">BEST-IN-CLASS 2.1 GAMING SPEAKER SYSTEM – Two powerful 2.75” satellite drivers with port-tube design 5.25” down-firing subwoofer.</span></li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 3px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">NATURAL SOUNDING WOODEN ENCLOSURES – Built entirely out of wood for better resonance damping, the enclosures deliver fuller, warmer, more natural sound than plastic-based designs.</span></li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 3px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">AUDIO CONTROLS – Control power and volume conveniently through the easy-access audio control pod. The pod also provides hassle-free connection for your headset and microphone.</span></li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 3px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">BLASTERX ACOUSTIC ENGINE – Choose between four presets and experience real-time audio enhancements like surround sound, clearer cues and bass boost.</span></li></ul><h3 style=\"margin-top: 1.29068em; margin-bottom: 0.840791em; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 24px; font-family: &quot;IBM Plex Sans&quot;; letter-spacing: -0.3px; line-height: 1.55; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Close Your Eyes, Take a Deep Breath and be Immersed in Total Audio Bliss</h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.41575em; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;IBM Plex Sans&quot;; font-size: 17px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">The Sound BlasterX Kratos S3 is packed with a pair of powerful 2.75” satellites and a port-tube design 5.25” down-firing subwoofer that are designed for gamers who need an entry-level gaming speaker system without compromising sound quality. This speaker system fulfills your audio needs from chilling out to your favorite movies and songs, to high-intensity all-out gaming warfare.</p><h3 style=\"margin-top: 1.29068em; margin-bottom: 0.840791em; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 24px; font-family: &quot;IBM Plex Sans&quot;; letter-spacing: -0.3px; line-height: 1.55; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Crafted for the Finest Acoustic</h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.41575em; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;IBM Plex Sans&quot;; font-size: 17px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Built entirely out of wood for better resonance damping, the Kratos S3 enclosures deliver fuller, warmer, more natural sound than plastic-based designs. The full-range satellites are optimized and designed with larger volume capacity to produce clear highs and detailed mid-range audio. The custom-tuned, down-firing subwoofer with port-tube design pumps out deep dynamic bass for massive gaming, superb movie and rich bass-centric music playback without distortion.</p><h3 style=\"margin-top: 1.29068em; margin-bottom: 0.840791em; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 24px; font-family: &quot;IBM Plex Sans&quot;; letter-spacing: -0.3px; line-height: 1.55; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Pwn the Battlefield</h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.41575em; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;IBM Plex Sans&quot;; font-size: 17px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Specially designed for the intense gamers, rev up your audio experience with 92 watts of pure power to give your entertainment or gameplay an extra “oomph”. Alternatively, you can connect to other media players via analog cable.</p><h3 style=\"margin-top: 1.29068em; margin-bottom: 0.840791em; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 24px; font-family: &quot;IBM Plex Sans&quot;; letter-spacing: -0.3px; line-height: 1.55; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Be in Control</h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.41575em; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;IBM Plex Sans&quot;; font-size: 17px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Adjust the volume control knob to bring out the best in your music, movies and games. Going for a scrim or perhaps some late night mayhem? Plug in any analog headset into the right satellite for a hassle-free change from speakers to something discreet.</p><h3 style=\"margin-top: 1.29068em; margin-bottom: 0.840791em; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 24px; font-family: &quot;IBM Plex Sans&quot;; letter-spacing: -0.3px; line-height: 1.55; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Sound BlasterX Acoustic Engine Lite</h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.41575em; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;IBM Plex Sans&quot;; font-size: 17px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;\">Although the speakers sounds great on their own, we have tapped into our rich history of creating class-leading audio algorithms to take the sound of the Kratos S3 beyond the realm of its physical limitations through audio enhancements optimized for your gameplaY.</p>', 0, 1, '6700', '6500', NULL, 0, '2021-08-31 20:27:43', '2021-09-21 15:07:28'),
