(538, 'Gamdias HERMES M6 Multi-color Backlit Mechanical Gaming Keyboard', 'gamdias-hermes-m6-mechanical-gaming-keyboard', '#609471780537', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'fast_deals', 'Fast Deals', 2, 14, 0, 1, 93, 'Gamdias-HERMES-M6-Multi-color-Backlit-Mechanical-Gaming-Keyboard86.jpg', 2, '<p><strong>KEY FEATURES:</strong></p><p>Model: HERMES M6<br>Seven built-in lighting effects and six color backlighting<br>GAMDIAS mechanical switches<br>Switch Type: Blue / Brown / Red / Black<br>Switch Lifecycle: 50 Million</p>', '<h3 style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">Gamdias HERMES M6 Multi-color Backlit Mechanical Gaming Keyboard</h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify;\">The Gamdias HERMES M6 comes with an elegant finish. It has been crafted meticulously with an aluminum bezel. The HERMES M6 proudly boasts its solid front plate and a refined metallic-textured touch-up on the edge of the keyboard while retaining its unique and aesthetically pleasing design. Bring vivid and brilliant illumination to the battlefield with seven built-in lighting effects and six color backlighting, along with two sky blue LED streaming lights on both wings of the keyboard to keep you in rhythm. Power through the battlegrounds with the GAMDIAS Certified Mechanical Gaming Switches, offering up to 50 million key presses while providing efficient and tactile feedback. It is a premium mechanical keyboard with a stylish posh metallic-textured brush-up backplate adjoined by two LED streaming lights matched with efficient and tactile feedback on each keystroke to help you get the job done. Blue / Brown / Red / Black Key Switch available with 50 Million Switch Lifecycle. It has a 1-year warranty.</p>', 0, 1, '3900', '3800', NULL, 0, '2021-09-03 00:18:55', '2021-09-17 08:27:21'),
(539, 'Gamdias HERMES P1B RGB Mechanical 3 in 1 Gaming Combo', 'gamdias-hermes-p1b-rgb-mechanical-3-in-1-gaming-combo', '#647086385538', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'fast_deals', 'Fast Deals', 2, 14, 0, 1, 93, 'Gamdias-HERMES-P1B-RGB-Mechanical-3-in-1-Gaming-Combo64.jpg', 1, '<p><strong>KEY FEATURES:</strong></p><p>Model: HERMES P1B<br>GAMDIAS Certified Mechanical Switches<br>Responsive Lighting<br>WASD and Arrow Keys Exchange<br>Anti-ghosting with N-key rollover</p>', '<h3 style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">Gamdias HERMES P1B RGB Mechanical 3 in 1 Gaming Combo</h3><h3 style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">Keyboard</h3><h4 style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Cable Length: 1.5m</h4><h4 style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Dimension(LxWxH) : 440 x140 x45mm</h4><h4 style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Interface : USB</h4><h4 style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Key Switch : GAMDIAS Certified Mechanical Switches</h4><h4 style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Switch Lifecycle : 50 Million</h4><h4 style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Weight : ≧895g</h4><h3 style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">Mouse</h3><h4 style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Cable Length : 1.3m</h4><h4 style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Connector : USB</h4><h4 style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Dimension(LxWxH) : 125 x 67 x 40 mm</h4><h4 style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Polling Rate : 125 HZ</h4><h4 style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Resolution : 1200/1600/ 2000/ 3200 DPI</h4><h4 style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Tracking Method : Advanced Gaming Optical Sensor</h4><h4 style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Weight : 110g</h4><h3 style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">Play Your Own Way</h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Featuring in 16.8 million RGB backlighting and 12 built-in lighting effects. The HERMES P1B mechanical keyboard provides many ways to interpret your style. There are 4 levels of brightness in RGB backlight with 10 additional multimedia keys. It is the gaming-elf of keyboards, which you have discovered.</p><p><img class=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.gamdias.com/gear/images/Gaming_Gear/COMBO/HERMES%20P1B%20COMBO/1_492X363/1.png\" data-src=\"\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"></p><h3 style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">Every Click Is an Amusement</h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Tapping on Gamdias’ certified mechanical switches, every click is an amusement. No matter how charged the battle is, you would dominate the situation precisely through its 100% anti-ghosting N-key rollover.</p><p><img class=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.gamdias.com/gear/images/Gaming_Gear/COMBO/HERMES%20P1B%20COMBO/2_492X363/2.png\" data-src=\"\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"></p><h3 style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">Snipe the Target</h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Maxing out at 3,200 dpi, the gaming mouse is adjustable on its accuracy through the centered control button on the mouse. The ergonomic design provides you an unprecedented gaming ambiance.</p><p><img class=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.gamdias.com/gear/images/Gaming_Gear/COMBO/HERMES%20P1B%20COMBO/3_492X363/3.png\" data-src=\"\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"></p><h3 style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">Anti-slip Mouse Mat</h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Double-layer fabrics provide a stable field on gameplays. The non-slip rubber back makes you confident in your mouse movement knowing that the mouse pad won’t budge an inch..</p><p><img class=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.gamdias.com/gear/images/Gaming_Gear/COMBO/HERMES%20P1B%20COMBO/4_492X363/4.png\" data-src=\"\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold;\">The&nbsp;Gamdias HERMES P1B RGB Mechanical 3 in 1 Gaming Combo has 1 Year of Replacement Warranty.</span><br></p>', 0, 1, '4500', '4300', NULL, 0, '2021-09-03 00:26:03', '2021-09-17 08:27:25');
